    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>高度自定制性能的读者墙<br />\ncss样式、短代码、展示数量完全可以自行定义</p>\n<p>同时插件提供默认的动态css设置，可以避免对css不熟悉用户的麻烦。</p>\n<p>简单易用，DEMO:<a href=\"http://blog.leniy.org/liuyan\" title=\"示例页面\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Leniy</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_donations&amp;business=HAENMLDR2UMFJ&amp;lc=US&amp;item_name=Leniy%20Plugins%20Donation&amp;item_number=plugin%2ddonate&amp;currency_code=USD&amp;bn=PP%2dDonationsBF%3abtn_donate_SM%2egif%3aNonHosted\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Donate link</a></p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Copy readers-wall.zip to your WordPress plugins directory, usually <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> and unzip the file.  It will create a <code>wp-content/plugins/readers-wall/</code> directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress.</li>\n<li>Follow the readers-wall page under options.</li>\n<li>Then, write the shortcode(et. [readerswall]) to a post/page.</li>\n</ol>\n",
        "faq": "<ul>\n<li>References:\n<ol>\n<li>Part of the css3 style from &#8220;Animated Buttons with CSS3&#8243;(Author:Anonymous)</li>\n<li>Part of Mysql code for counting of the comments came from 百度知道</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ul>\n",
